{"tid":1327122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］721會出嘅麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-17T12:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:28:10.000Z","uid":18648,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3396d91c0dccad23c75a7bcd9342c6f1ca36e24a","tid":1327122,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"721如果射完摧淚彈我地都唔走<br />\n有好大機會出水炮車<br />\n<br />\n係哩段時間內<br />\n我地要諗好應對方法<br />\n<br />\n如果當日大家明顯唔齊Gear<br />\n一出水炮我地真係要散水或者轉場<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千萬不能戀戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都好撚勇<br />\n想同班狗死過<br />\n<br />\n但單靠精靈球<br />\n我地無可能同水炮車打<br />\n<br />\n如果我地哩段時間內都諗唔到應對方法<br />\n一係轉場轉去多市民嘅地方<br />\n例如旺角尖咀<br />\n<br />\n69到今日 被捕嘅義士超過一百個<br />\n雨革魚旦更多唔洗講<br />\n真係唔可以再有人犧牲<br />\n前線只會越來越少人<br />\n贏面就越來越細<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下<br />\n一出水炮車我地點搞喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48346ad11a13d7080a135f64475c2b2e9e77882","tid":1327122,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"［前線入]對於Gear有少少建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d6ca59f256b0a3f44e721729f0f0f34e65e7681","tid":1327122,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe0a9124d22a2413f0facb8758a45115e9d1a94","tid":1327122,"uid":111375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"轉場再戰一齊搭車嗰吓好難攪"},{"pid":"95ee6529da70117f4eccb91ba3e5f0b876c304da","tid":1327122,"uid":18648,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fbe0a9124d22a2413f0facb8758a45115e9d1a94","tid":1327122,"uid":111375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"轉場再戰一齊搭車嗰吓好難攪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13: